{"word":"H2685 - חֲצַף - chătsaph - khats-af' - Hasty","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֲצַף</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chătsaph"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khats-af'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Hasty"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அவசரமாய்பிற, கடுமையாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Aphel) to be urgent, to be harsh, to show insolence"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (Chaldee); a primitive root; properly to <i>shear</i> or cut close; figuratively to <i>be severe: - </i>hasty, be urgent."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}